title: Business Applications with Planned Wages for Texas (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BAWBATOTALNSATX (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BAWBATOTALNSATX) for an alternative.

High-Propensity Business Applications (HBA) that indicate a first wages‐paid date on the IRS Form SS-4. The indication of a wages-paid date is associated with a high likelihood of transitioning into a business with payroll.
